body.description: Shea Moisture hair care for Kids offers a Mango & Carrot Extra-Nourishing Shampoo that gently cleanses and detangles fine and delicate hair; this shea shampoo is the best shampoo for all kids. A top-notch moisturizing shampoo and cruelty-free shampoo that bathes young hair strands in nourishing Coconut Oil and Olive Oil along with certified organic Shea Butter found in our shampoo. Made with Carrot, Mango and Citrus Extracts, our sulfate free shampoo, shea butter shampoo and coconut shampoo offers kid-friendly illuminating brightness and enhanced curl definition. While nourishing hair is important with this hydrating shampoo, strengthening hair is also a main focus for our kids coconut shampoo; use on dry hair and as a hair treatment to their weak strands. This hair shampoo for kids by Shea Moisture is a carefully formulated clarifying shampoo and hydrating shampoo that contains no silicones, no sulfates, no parabens, no phthalates, no mineral oil or petrolatum. Treat kids' natural hair with this coconut oil shampoo, shea butter shampoo and dry hair treatment that has been tested on family and friends and never animals. To shampoo hair using fingertips, gently massage coconut shampoo through wet hair. Rinse hair shampoo with warm water. Follow with Shea Moisture Kid's Extra-Nourishing Conditioner. Our Story: SheaMoisture is the legacy of Sofi Tucker, a pioneering mother of four and an entrepreneur, who sold Shea Butter, African Black Soap and homemade beauty preparations in Sierra Leone in 1912. We honor her vision by continuing to formulate with Raw Shea Butter handcrafted by women in Africa. With every purchase, you show support of our mission to reinvest back in our communities.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 21, 2021
reviews.reviewText: We absolutely love this shampoo! I have two boys with very different hair. The oldest is 6 and has thick, wavy hair that doesn’t usually dry out. My younger son is almost two, and has curly, dry hair that needs moisture and a very sensitive scalp.I was looking for something “more” than Johnson & Johnson and all of the other baby shampoos out there because my younger son’s hair was feeling fried constantly. I bought this two months ago and it works GREAT for both boys! My younger son’s hair is moisturized and healthy—and bonus—he hasn’t had any scalp irritation whatsoever since we started using this! My older son likes the smell and it leaves his hair soft and healthy looking.The smell of this shampoo is also divine! I was surprised to read that someone found it “perfume-y” because it actually has a light, natural scent. It says on the ingredients label that it was scented with essential oils, and it smells like orange blossom and a little vanilla? Whatever it is, it smells great!Highly recommend!!
